 |archive-date    = 2019-06-15
 |archive-url     = https://web.archive.org/web/20190615060508/http://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/pdf/2003/26/aah4157.pdf
}}</ref>。

2016年3月，聯合{{link-en|AIP|Leibniz Institute for Astrophysics Potsdam}}、[[約翰霍普金斯大學|JHU]]和巴恩斯以及其他人等在20顆類太陽恆星的自轉週期上的一項研究，通過星點移動對光度曲線的影響來衡量，表明這些大約40億年的恆星旋轉周期大約為26天，就像我們的太陽在赤道處的週期為25.38天<ref>
{{cite journal
 |author=Sydney A. Barnes |author2=Jörg Weingrill |author3=Dario Fritzewski |author4=Klaus G. Strassmeier |author5=Imants Platais
 |date=2016
 |title=Rotation periods for cool stars in the 4 Gyr-old open cluster M67, the solar-stellar connection, and the applicability of gyrochronology to at least solar age
 |journal=[[The_Astrophysical_Journal|The Astrophysical Journal]]
 |volume=823 |issue=1 |pages=16
 |arxiv=1603.09179
 |bibcode=2016ApJ...823...16B
 |doi=10.3847/0004-637X/823/1/16
}}</ref>。這些測量是[[克卜勒太空望遠鏡|克卜勒太空望遠鏡]]擴展的{{link-en|K2任務| Kepler (spacecraft)#Second Light (K2)}}任務中完成的。這加强了太陽的許多關鍵性質對相同大小和年齡恒星的適用性，這是現代[[天體物理學|太陽]]和[[恒星物理學|恒星物理學]]的基本[[原理|原理]]<ref name="Astronomy Now">{{cite web|url=http://astronomynow.com/2016/05/17/stars-nearly-as-old-as-sun-found-to-have-similar-spin-rates|title=Stars nearly as old as Sun found to have similar spin rates|publisher=Astronomy Now|language=en|date=17 May 2016|access-date=2022-04-09|archive-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210518202505/https://astronomynow.com/2016/05/17/stars-nearly-as-old-as-sun-found-to-have-similar-spin-rates/}}</ref>。作者將其縮寫為「太陽 - 恆星連接」<ref name="Astronomy Now"/>。

